 The couple A video has captured the adorable moment a woman popped the big question to her lover in a mall and he accepted the proposal. In the short clip, contrary to the conventional manner of men proposing to their women, the lady took out her ring, knelt down and inserted the ring into her man’s finger amid cheers. The love birds further shared a kiss after the lady arose with smiles on her face. Watch The Video Below: In what seems to be an awkward display, social media users have shown surprise over the lady’s action. Others however support the lady’s move. See Reactions Below; 